        <item>
            <title>1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 14:55:00 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Resume Claude Code sessions</b> — pick up any session you started in Terminal, scoped to the current project or all projects.</li>
                    <li><b>Context usage bar</b> — live percentage of model context, with a one-click <b>Compact</b> button at 80%.</li>
                    <li><b>Jump to latest</b> — floating button when you've scrolled up; chat no longer jumps to the top on its own.</li>
                    <li><b>Menubar status</b> — yellow pulsing typing dots while working, green bubble when a reply is waiting.</li>
                    <li><b>Remote Control bridge</b> — open the active session in your browser at claude.ai/code from the directory bar.</li>
                    <li><b>Auto permission mode</b> — auto-approves safe tools, prompts for risky ones.</li>
                    <li><b>Send Feedback</b> — direct line from the About window or right-click menu.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
